replaceView

DNSView replaceView(DNSView view)
Replaces a new view object as child of this top level component. If it is not present it is just added. We gave it an attribute equal to its name, and if it is a "default" view, we also bound it with the DEFAULT_VIEW attribute.

Parameters:
view - A view data object that replaces/adds.
Returns:
The old view with the same name or null.
